Type of Feat: Class
Prerequisite: Swordsage, level 20.
Specifics: When you reach 20th level, you can use two boost maneuvers simultaneously. Whenever you initiate a boost maneuver, you can also initiate any other boost maneuver that you know as a free action. Both boosts you initiate are expended normally. You can use this ability three times per day.

Use: Selected.  For a single round you can initiate two boosts.
